class Testabc:
    def __init__(self, prediction: int):
        self.prediction = prediction
        
    def __lt__(self, p1):
        prob1 = self.prediction
        prob2 = p1.prediction
        return prob1 < prob2
    
    def __le__(self, p1):
        prob1 = self.prediction
        prob2 = p1.prediction
        return prob1 <= prob2
    
    def __eq__(self, p1): 
        prob1 = self.prediction
        prob2 = p1.prediction
        return prob1 == prob2
    
    def __ne__(self, p1): 
        prob1 = self.prediction
        prob2 = p1.prediction
        return prob1 != prob2
    
    def __gt__(self, p1): 
        prob1 = self.prediction
        prob2 = p1.prediction
        return prob1 > prob2
    
    def __ge__(self, p1): 
        prob1 = self.prediction
        prob2 = p1.prediction
        return prob1 >= prob2
    
    def __str__(self):
        return str(self.prediction)
